data.text:
Welcome to our Southside office, located at the intersection of JTB and Belfort Road (Quadrant Complex).

For parking, please use the main entrance, the first right turn into the complex, and park in the lot on the right. Additional handicapped parking is to the left (after turning right into the main complex).
